### ========================================
### SCHEDULE ENDPOINTS
### ========================================

### PUBLIC ROUTE - Get Weekly Schedule (No Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules/weekly

### ========================================
### PROTECTED ROUTES (Require Token)
### ========================================

### 1. Create Schedule
# @name createSchedule
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "programId": "{{programId}}",
  "dayOfWeek": 3,
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "endTime": "14:00"
}

### 2. Get All Schedules
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Schedule by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Update Schedule - Full
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "programId": "{{programId}}",
  "dayOfWeek": 4,
  "startTime": "11:00",
  "endTime": "15:00"
}

### 5. Update Schedule - Partial (only times)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "12:00",
  "endTime": "16:00"
}

### 6. Update Schedule - Partial (only day)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": 5
}

### 7. Delete Schedule
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Delete ALL Schedules (toda la programación)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### EXAMPLES FOR DIFFERENT DAYS
### ========================================

### Monday (dayOfWeek: 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "programId": "{{programId}}",
  "dayOfWeek": 1,
  "startTime": "08:00",
  "endTime": "10:00"
}

### Tuesday (dayOfWeek: 2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "programId": "{{programId}}",
  "dayOfWeek": 2,
  "startTime": "14:00",
  "endTime": "16:00"
}

### Saturday (dayOfWeek: 6)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "programId": "{{programId}}",
  "dayOfWeek": 6,
  "startTime": "20:00",
  "endTime": "23:00"
}

### Sunday (dayOfWeek: 0)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "programId": "{{programId}}",
  "dayOfWeek": 0,
  "startTime": "18:00",
  "endTime": "22:00"
}

### ========================================
### ERROR CASES
### ========================================

### Invalid day of week (> 6)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "programId": "{{programId}}",
  "dayOfWeek": 7,
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}

### Invalid time format
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "programId": "{{programId}}",
  "dayOfWeek": 1,
  "startTime": "25:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}

### Non-existent program (or program from another station)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "programId": "invalid-program-id",
  "dayOfWeek": 1,
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}

### Missing required fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": 1,
  "startTime": "10:00"
}

### Without authentication
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}/schedules

### Invalid stationId
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/invalid-station-id/schedules/weekly

### ========================================
### DAY OF WEEK REFERENCE
### ========================================
# 0 = Domingo (Sunday)
# 1 = Lunes (Monday)
# 2 = Martes (Tuesday)
# 3 = Miércoles (Wednesday)
# 4 = Jueves (Thursday)
# 5 = Viernes (Friday)
# 6 = Sábado (Saturday)